    }
  ],
  "actionable_ascii_heavy_residuals": [],
  "accepted_ascii_heavy_residuals": [
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:1",
      "text": "某些站点可能希望在 upgrading 前备份 job data。这样做有两个好处：backup 可以在 upgrade 期间发生意外问题（例如 software 或 hardware failure）时防止 historical job data 丢失；另外，如果需要 downgrade，system 可以恢复到 pre-upgrade state。Backups 和 downgrades 会在下文讨论。",
      "ascii_letters": 116,
      "cjk_chars": 57
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:3",
      "text": "执行 upgrade 所需时间主要受修改 database schema 所需 operations 影响。特定 upgrade 的 documentation 会提示何时可能需要较长时间（例如超过一分钟）来执行 upgrade。Upgrade 期间，active tasks 可以继续运行；不过不会 schedule 新 work，不能 submit 新 jobs，Dashboard、command-line 和 API 与 engine 的通信会 block。",
      "ascii_letters": 132,
      "cjk_chars": 63
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:4",
      "text": "备份操作说明（Backing Up）",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:5",
      "text": "备份 job database 前，请确保 tractor engine 和 postgresql database 已停止。除非站点在其 db.config 文件中将 DBShutdown 设置为 False，或 engine 难以与 database server 通信，否则 engine 会自动关闭 database server。",
      "ascii_letters": 105,
      "cjk_chars": 36
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:6",
      "text": "tractor-dbctl",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:9",
      "text": "tractor-dbctl",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:12",
      "text": "要备份 job database，请运行",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:13",
      "text": "tractor-dbctl",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:15",
      "text": "<path-to-backup-file>",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:16",
      "text": "。请确保有足够空间存储 backup file。Backup file 是 engine data directory 的 psql/ subdirectory 的 compressed tarball，因此只需要该 directory 所用空间的一小部分。",
      "ascii_letters": 81,
      "cjk_chars": 28
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:17",
      "text": "降级操作说明（Downgrading）",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:18",
      "text": "Downgrading 时，如果现有 database 已经历 schema change，可能无法继续使用。在这种情况下，需要从新的 job database 开始，或从 backup restore。如果必须保留 upgrade 后发生的 job submissions 和 state changes，请联系 Customer Support。",
      "ascii_letters": 103,
      "cjk_chars": 45
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:20",
      "text": "Backing Up",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:21",
      "text": "所述停止现有 engine 和 database server。然后用以下命令 destroy job database：",
      "ascii_letters": 38,
      "cjk_chars": 14
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:22",
      "text": "tractor-dbctl",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:25",
      "text": "要从 backup restore job database，请使用",
      "ascii_letters": 24,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:26",
      "text": "tractor-dbctl",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:28",
      "text": "<path-to-backup-file>",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:29",
      "text": "并以适用版本的 engine 启动；job IDs 会从创建 backup 时最后使用的 job ID 继续。Backup 时处于 queued 状态的 jobs 会在 system 恢复到 backup 后重新 scheduled。Backup 之后提交的 jobs 不会出现在 restored job database 中。",
      "ascii_letters": 89,
      "cjk_chars": 46
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:30",
      "text": "如果 job database 没有从 backup restore，它就只是一个空 job database，job IDs 从 1 开始。",
      "ascii_letters": 41,
      "cjk_chars": 15
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:31",
      "text": "注意，如果 job ID 被 reused，其 log file output 会 append 到之前同 ID job 的 log files 中。因此，建议移除与将被 reused 的 job IDs 相关的 log files。",
      "ascii_letters": 63,
      "cjk_chars": 26
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:32",
      "text": "Job ID sequence 可以从不同 value 恢复，以避免 reusing job IDs。首先用以下命令启动 database server：",
      "ascii_letters": 45,
      "cjk_chars": 19
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:33",
      "text": "tractor-dbctl",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:34",
      "text": "--start-for-engine",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:36",
      "text": "tractor-dbctl",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:37",
      "text": "--set-job-counter",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:39",
      "text": "在 Dashboard admin panel 管理面板中暂停 dispatching 调度。",
      "ascii_letters": 30,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:40",
      "text": "Retry 重试所有 active tasks 活动任务：tq",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:43",
      "text": "retry active",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:45",
      "text": "Destroy job database：",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:46",
      "text": "tractor-dbctl",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:48",
      "text": "可选地 restore 恢复 backed up database 备份数据库：",
      "ascii_letters": 23,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:49",
      "text": "tractor-dbctl",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:51",
      "text": "<path-to-backup-file>",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:52",
      "text": "Start 启动 database server：",
      "ascii_letters": 19,
      "cjk_chars": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:53",
      "text": "tractor-dbctl",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:54",
      "text": "--start-for-engine",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:56",
      "text": "tractor-dbctl",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:57",
      "text": "--show-params",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:58",
      "text": "并移除 job ID 更高的 jobs 的任何 log files。",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 9
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:59",
      "text": "可选地设置 job counter：",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:60",
      "text": "tractor-dbctl",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:61",
      "text": "--set-job-counter",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:62",
      "text": "Start 启动适用的 engine。",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:63",
      "text": "注意，这里描述的所有 tractor-dbctl commands 都需要使用 --configdir option 指定 site configuration directory。",
      "ascii_letters": 61,
      "cjk_chars": 16
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:64",
      "text": "多个 Engines 引擎说明（Multiple Engines）",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:65",
      "text": "可以同时运行不同版本的 Tractor engines，例如在部署到 production 前测试新版本。多个 engines 可以在同一 host 上运行；不过它们必须具有不同的 ports、configuration directories、data directories 和 database directories。即使 engines 不在同一 host 上运行，只要它们对上述任一 directories 使用相同的 network-sharable volumes，就可能发生 corruption。这里重要的 configuration settings 是 tractor.config 中的 TractorDataDirectory 和 db.config 中的 DBDataDir。还需要管理不同的 log files locations，以及让 blades 指向合适的 engine。",
      "ascii_letters": 252,
      "cjk_chars": 100
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:66",
      "text": "附加信息说明（Additional Information）",
      "ascii_letters": 21,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:67",
      "text": "有关特定版本的 upgrade information，请参阅以下 documents。",
      "ascii_letters": 27,
      "cjk_chars": 12
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:68",
      "text": "Upgrading from 1.x",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:69",
      "text": "Upgrading to 2.1",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "9050f49616:70",
      "text": "Upgrading to 2.2",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    }
